```plantuml
@startuml geovanegodoi_MicroServicesPOC

actor Client
participant "Catalog Microservice" as Catalog
participant "Customer Microservice" as Customer
participant "Order Microservice" as Order
participant "RabbitMQ" as RabbitMQ
database "MongoDB (Catalog)" as MongoCatalog
database "MongoDB (Customer)" as MongoCustomer
database "MongoDB (Order)" as MongoOrder

== Deployment Phase ==
Client -> Catalog: HTTP POST /api/catalogitems
activate Catalog
Catalog -> MongoCatalog: Create catalog item
Catalog --> RabbitMQ: Publish CatalogItemCreated event
deactivate Catalog

Client -> Customer: HTTP POST /api/customers
activate Customer
Customer -> MongoCustomer: Create customer
Customer --> RabbitMQ: Publish CustomerCreated event
deactivate Customer

== Order Processing Flow ==
Client -> Order: HTTP POST /api/orders
activate Order
Order -> MongoOrder: Create order
Order --> RabbitMQ: Publish OrderCreated event
deactivate Order

RabbitMQ -> Customer: OrderCreated event
activate Customer
Customer -> MongoCustomer: Update customer order history
deactivate Customer

RabbitMQ -> Catalog: OrderCreated event
activate Catalog
Catalog -> MongoCatalog: Update catalog item availability
deactivate Catalog

== Eventual Consistency ==
loop Event Processing
    RabbitMQ -> Customer: CatalogItemUpdated event
    activate Customer
    Customer -> MongoCustomer: Update local catalog cache
    deactivate Customer
    
    RabbitMQ -> Order: CustomerUpdated event
    activate Order
    Order -> MongoOrder: Update local customer cache
    deactivate Order
end

@enduml
```